### Triggers

Prefer this tool when any of the following apply:

- User or agent explicitly names `cron_tick_snapshot` or equivalent (cron tick snapshot)
- Workflow step that matches this capability: cron tick snapshot
- Start of a scheduled agent tick: one JSON bundle of planner ready tasks, loops/blockers, approvals, spec rollup, ledger open runs, optional queue depth.
- Scheduled tick: single snapshot of planner + loops + approvals + specs + ledger + queue depth
- End-of-tick checkpoint: loop_step and/or ledger append in one call

### Summary

Start of a scheduled agent tick: one JSON bundle of planner ready tasks, loops/blockers, approvals, spec rollup, ledger open runs, optional queue depth.

## How to use

- Required: `project`. Tune `ready_task_limit`, `loop_limit`, `approval_limit`, `ledger_open_limit`, `include_prompt_queue`, `hint_format`.

## Project

Pass the same stable `project` string on every tool call for this mount (alphanumeric start; then letters, digits, `.`, `_`, `-`).
